Phrase: With Blackfriar leading the way, the SSS have arrived at the location of the portal.
Islington told us that the portal would not close if there was a person inside, but there was no sign of the person who had entered the portal. This means that they are still inside.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: So this is the hidden portal. What in the world is going on inside?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: According to the information of those who have entered, it is a large station-like place.

Name: Putra
Phrase: A big train station? I think the train station we used as a base was pretty big, does that mean this here's bigger than that?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: If there's a gate, it means there's a connection from there to another place.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Why did this portal suddenly appear out of nowhere?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Firstly this is just a conjecture on my part...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: But I think it's probably because there's someone in here right now. This portal appeared shortly after she came to my unit.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Blackfriar, you let a new recruit who just joined the Out-Siders enter this portal, right? Isn't that a bit harsh?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: I didn't order her to do it. She insisted by her own volition.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Not to worry, the newcomer is stronger than me in fact. In fact I think the only person who can beat her is Ohana.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: She's stronger than you, Blackfriar?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Aye. Frustrating, I know, but she's stronger than me. There is no one better qualified for this mission than her.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: So many strong people have been in the Out-Siders...".

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: But ma'am, this new cadet isn't just any new cadet, is she?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: If there exists someone this strong, Islington wouldn't be silent. She would have been given her all sorts of jobs much earlier.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Well, well, well, you're as sharp as they say you are. Judging from your looks, I even suspect that you already have an idea of who she is, yes?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Almost. But Yoshino is too kind to tell everyone.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Vivienne, any ideas?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: No clue. Why is Yoshino always so smart?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: That's because Yoshino is a clever, cute, kougyoukei, textile-weaving, sorcery-casting, kemomimi girl.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Grrr, darn it! Don't wag your tail like you're so proud of yourself~!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: If Miss Yoshino knows who she is, is she someone we know?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: There's not much clues, as the Out-Siders are all strong. Likely someone who might want to join the Out-Siders.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Got it!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Eh! Yakky too! Yakky's a brainy type too!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Why didn't she come out sooner? She's strong enough to get into the Out-Siders. The only Knight of St. Iris with that much potential is that person!

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Yoshino, please don't say anything. I'll definitely say it first. I'm not kidding, okay?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ooooh, Yakutsk is always good at these.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: So who is she?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I'll tell you right off the bat. This new member is...".

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Detroit!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Oh, yeah! Well, it could certainly be Miss Detroit!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Shame. Your answer's incorrect♪

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: No?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: No, not even close.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Bah, I got it wrong?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: I'm not saying it's impossible to be anyone else but Detroit. I just mentioned one of the possibilities, I did not assert...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: The correct answer is Mary Rosegarden~

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Mary Rosegarden...

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Mary Rosegarden...

Name: Putra
Phrase: Mary Rosegarden...

Name: Putra
Phrase: What, THE Mary Rosegarden~! Mary is that person, right~? She was the Knight Commander of St. Iris, right~? Aha, I concede that I didn't know who~

Name: Putra
Phrase: Wait What? What is going on!? Mary Rosegarden, you, you!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Calm down, Putra! Your face is really creepy! Yes your delayed straight-man comedy is impressive, but a girl shouldn't make faces like that!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: How did Rosa... Mary end up in the Out-Siders?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Islington's arranged her to team up with us temporarily. She has her own goals to reach the Giant Tree, and she has promised not to mess with the Knights of the Order or the SSS anymore.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: However, what did the higher-ups say about allowing an ex-Resistance member within our ranks? Isn't that going beyond the authority of a Divine Child?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: That's taken into account, because we submitted the reports as 'the missing Knight Commander' instead.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Well, past records indicated that Mary Rosegarden disappeared into the Phantom Mist while on duty...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The main point is that Mary Rosegarden is now reemployed as an Out-Sider.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Verily, I still don't trust her. She might betray and attack us once she gets inside the Tree. She has that much power. If she becomes our enemy, she won't be so easy to stop.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Personally I think the best thing to do is to lock her up in a prison cell...".

Name: Queensway
Phrase: I disagree. She has helped us many times. She's also the one who told us about The Giant Tree Route Map.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Well, she volunteered for a dangerous mission to gain my trust, so I guess that's saaayin~ something.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Mary is fighting alone in the face of unknown horrors. Whatever her background was, her courage and fighting ability are a marvel to behold.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Rosa's in there...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: ...Queensway.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Mention the name 'Rosa' in front of me ever again, and I'll give you a brutal pummeling, capiche?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Ah...

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Everything you believed previously will amount to nothing but impermanence and regret.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: You will obey my command absolutely and affirmatively. Is that clear?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Yes, sir! Affirmative!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Hmmhmm, that's good to hear.

Name: Fayette
Phrase: Instructor Blackfriar. The perimeter of the portal has been secured. We can still sense magic in there, so we believe Mary is currently safe.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: But the portal appears to be weakening considerably. I think she's having trouble controlling it from the inside.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Everybody, we're going in. As soon as the first person enters, the next will follow in quick succession.

Name: Fayette
Phrase: Perhaps you should decide on the order of entry. When Mary came in, the portal closed immediately.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: If that's the case, that's still too slow.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Everyone to charge in at the same time! everyone!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Same time!?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Huddle round in front of the portal. Our formation should be as small as possible.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Yes, here we go!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: What? Putra, where are you grabbing me?

Name: Putra
Phrase: Your tummy!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Not my tummy! You should grab my chest or hips!

Name: Putra
Phrase: The chest it is!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yakky-tan, come on, grab me tighter. Grab Yoshino like you do when you sleep.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: This is not the time to say that!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: On my count, we all are to charge in at once. 3... 2... 1, GO!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Whoa! We're floating!

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Stay calm. It seems like we're only currently 'teleported' somewhere.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Could this be similar to Gate magic?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Yes, it could be. I don't know, I've never actually been in one, but it kind of feels like it.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Hah, this is a precious and lovely experience. Mary must be seeing such sights then.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: (She's... smiling... When we don't know where we're going)

Name: Queensway
Phrase: (I understand now. Miss Blackfriar is already ready to do this, I'm sure she has bet her life many times before. Bets where she doesn't even know if she'll be alive...).
After we entered the portal in the middle of the forest, we soon find ourselves in a landscape completely different from anything we had ever seen before.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Oho, so this is what it looks like inside.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Firstly, the density of the Mist is off the charts. I can't believe she kept fighting all night long in the middle of this place. Mary must have been pretty good at it.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: It's Mary!

Name: Mary
Phrase: Queensway! You're safe!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Ro... Mary!

Name: Mary
Phrase: I'm so glad you made it all the way out here. I knew you would come.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Of course I did. If I had known Mary was here, I would have rushed over sooner.

Name: Putra
Phrase: It's an emotional reunion, isn't it? Queensway looks so happy.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Understandable since she went missing after we separated back at the station.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: I have a bad feeling about this.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: A bad feeling?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: I'm surprised that you're working together with the Out-Siders. Do you intend to continue your service with Lady Islington?

Name: Mary
Phrase: Yes, I intend to. I want to fight with you in together and I'll look forward to working with you then.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: But Mary, you said you have your own objectives, right? You said that you'll work with us until we reach the Giant Tree, what will you do after that...?

Name: Mary
Phrase: It's true that I have my own agenda. But even after we get to the Giant Tree, I will still be your partner. This will never change. Once I can get the recognition of the Out-Siders, we may be together for a long time to come.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Is that true...!?

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Of course not, it's all codswallop.

Name: Mary
Phrase: ...Gwargh?
The moment when Queensway and Mary stepped towards each other to hug each other and rejoice in their emotional reunion
--A slender sword impaled Mary's abdomen.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Mary!

Name: Mary
Phrase: That's, impossible... Why are you betraying me here...?

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Mary! Pull yourself together!
It was her own rapier that stabbed her. Of course, her rapier did not move on its own.
The person who stabbed Mary took advantage of a momentary lull in the situation to take it from her. Even Queensway, who had Mary in her sights, could not react at all.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: She didn't get hit anywhere vital. She's not going to die.

Name: Blackfriar
Phrase: Queensway. Stay away from this woman now. That's an order.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Miss Blackfriar...?
The person who stabbed Mary... was Blackfriar.
